re guidé par des personnes compétentes et expérimentées. Les auteurs verseront à Centraide les redevances découlant de la vente du livre.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 7aPSYCHOLOGY / General.2bisacsh1 aBastien, Célyne H., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBelleville, Geneviève, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlanchette, Isabelle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoisvert, Jean-Marie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBonneau, Simon Beaulieu, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBorges, Lucienne Martins, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBoudreault, Véronique, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrisset, Camille, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrochu, Émilie Fortier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBusque, Guillaume Foldes, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBégin, Catherine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaron, Laurence, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCeklic, Tijana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCellard, Caroline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChartier, Isabelle Soucy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCloutier, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDenis, Isabelle, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDiguer, Louis, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDionne, Ginette, econtributor.4ctb4https://i